data.description: $$Assumable 2.75% FHA$$From the moment you arrive you’ll be delighted by the attention to detail! Lush landscaping including a lovely focal bridge & stone accents lead to the covered porch entry.Distinguished home includes designer fixtures & finishes including tile, warm wood flooring & custom shutters. Living/Dining Room has soaring windows w/ open staircase providing a warm & elegant space. The heart of the home; the spacious kitchen has beautiful granite counters, backsplash, SS Appliances & an island perfect for hosting family & friends. Expansive great room w/ open design provides effortless flow & room to entertain*Dble doors lead to space for an office or studio, you decide*3 car garage features workbenches & storage*Private yard w/ citrus trees is perfect for dining al fresco or relaxing in the spa*Upstairs, the loft provides abundant of space for movies or games & the elegant primary suite features a sitting room & a spa inspired ensuite*Nearby Shopping, Dining, 95/215 access
